S.FORM: Alexander Van der Bellen Aliksanta Fantipilon I 1944 miheca saka 1 folad saka 18 a romi'ad sofocen ci Alisanta Fanter Peylon, malamikomoday a tamdaw. I 2016 miheca saka 12 folad saka 4 romi'ad miliyaw a misinkiw to congtong ko Awtili, itira i sakacecay royad a mitopa pakaala to 54% to satopa maala malacontong no Awtili. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Austria anini i ci Alisanta Fanter Peylon, patirengan a romi'ad i 2017 a miheca saka 1 folad saka 26 a romi'ad. 1 2020 miheca saka 5 folad saka 24 romi'ad misalafii a mili'epah ato widang i kakomaenan i maci, mico'isay to sapi'ading to lifong to rikec, orasaka,macepet no tayhin. Österreich: Van der Bellen wird Bundespräsident. Frankfurter Allgemeine Zeitung. Van der Bellen gewinnt die Wahl. Wiener Zeitung. (2016-12-04). (原始內容存檔於2017-03-05). laloma'an 家庭 Pinaro no loma' ni Alisanta Fanter Peylon , O teloc no Sarawa'an no Rosiya , iraay ho ko no Horan a kasarocorocok no 'ilang1944 miheca saka 1 folad saka 18 romi'ad itini i Wiyiena no Awtili ko kahofoc ningra. I 1994 a miheca tangasa i 2012 a miheca, o miocoran no Langdaway-Centang a malakiing no Finawlan-Pikaikiaan no Kitakit . Malakakeridan no Langdaway-Centang ato citodongay to demak no kiing cingra. lalamod 配偶 Safaw falo ko mihecaan i, pataloma' to ci Alisanta Fanter Peylon , safaw siwa ko mihecaan nira malamama' to. Ci Policiter Peyelay ko fafahi nira, nai 1943-2018 miheca 50 a mihecaan ko ka lalamod nangra, nikaorira, itini to 2015 a miheca malalikong cangra, tatosa ko fa'inayan a wawa nangra. Itiya sato i 2015 miheca saka safaw tosa a folad, pataloma' heca to toya widang nira ci Toris Semitawer , itini to i Wiyena ato Kaneytar ko aro' nangra. palatamdaw 教育 Itini i 1966 miheca, oya nitilidan mikikiwan nira a kicaci ato ya ono sowse nira a tilid hananay hawi, pakalayap to sakakaay tata'akay a ngangan to Hakasi/Pose . I 1970 miheca itira i Yinspoluko Taikaku a malaciyawso(singsi)nipasifa' to sapili'etan a kicai. mikapot to sieci政治 Nai tenokay no 1970 a miheca tangesa i ikor no1980 a miheca, ci Alisanta Fanter Peylon mikapotay to Siyakay-Finawlan Centang no Awtili , nikaorira, mafalic to ko hareteng pasayra i midipotay to salawacan laylay a ko demak ningra. Keriden noya pakafanaan nira a mitiliday ci Pitiro Pilec a mikomod tonini kangdaway-Centang , o kahatini kafalic tona demak i, matilid itini to misalolongan a tilid ningra. pitooran 宗教 Kapah ho ci Alisanta Fanter Peylon , miliyas to Fokoing-Kiwkay pakayni to sowal no poksi ira ko caay ka pakaso^lin to kawas, Nikaorira, pakaso^lin to"Ratoh anca o Mapolosi"(Botschaft oder Vision) cingra, saharaterateng han nira i, o nini ko tadaso^linay/fa^lohay a katatelekan a pitooran. Orasaka itini to 2019 a miheca mipawacay to pitooran ningra, miliyaw to a mikapot tona Fokoing-Kiwkay no Akesepow . Van der Bellen, Alexander (30 April 2019). "„Die Botschaft des Neuen Testaments ist mir wichtig"". Sonntagsblatt . Archived from the original on 6 July 2019. Retrieved 1 May 2019. "Van der Bellen wieder in Evangelische Kirche eingetreten" . Der Standard.
